                            <comment id="14982254" author="blambov" created="Fri, 30 Oct 2015 09:50:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch uploaded &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/blambov/cassandra/tree/9223&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. Cancels batchlog replay cycle if the storage service doesn&apos;t know about any nodes and adds a unit test.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14984604" author="stefania" created="Mon, 2 Nov 2015 00:10:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CI is here:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/blambov/job/blambov-9223-testall/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/blambov/job/blambov-9223-testall/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
